metadata.name: Water child #1
metadata.description:
"Water child" collection is a creative symbiosis of different arts. 
That's the case when my team and I was creating the project all summer long. Many stages of preparation were passed. From the portrait filming on various films, to creation of the soundtrack and the filming in the water. 
This collection is the meditative formula that everyone is looking for, because the most important thing in our lives is a peace of mind.

Photographer Victoria Khlebova
